{"id": "ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw", "rating": 4.6, "userRatingCount": 1164, "displayName": {"text": "Arsicault Bakery", "languageCode": "en"}, "editorialSummary": {"text": "Trendy bakeshop with modern decor offering typical French fare like croissants & quiche.", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25vNU5FVnFhRGs0YTNodk9HdDBhRk5TYVhGa1RIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Arsicault Bakery was exceptional! The cinnamon croissant and all our pastries were insanely good, and the Londoner sandwich was delicious too. Great café lattes and worth the ~10-minute line, supper fresh and delicious. Highly recommended!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Arsicault Bakery was exceptional! The cinnamon croissant and all our pastries were insanely good, and the Londoner sandwich was delicious too. Great café lattes and worth the ~10-minute line, supper fresh and delicious. Highly recommended!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Remi Tayar", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109724233062099123728/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXfsV-vkwKVeNGTKzLA2It9VMkryu8KyxIj55qoTjt-lpdK1_rC=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-01T18:49:12.141357976Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25vNU5FVnFhRGs0YTNodk9HdDBhRk5TYVhGa1RIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25vNU5FVnFhRGs0YTNodk9HdDBhRk5TYVhGa1RIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858112994842f7:0xac8648260314bc5e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGNE1rWkRVSE16V1VSVU16RkZVMGd4WnpZNWRtYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Ok, this is in a somewhat seedy area of town ( the Tenderloin has some notoriety). And while you see homeless etc, during the day it is bustling with people.\nThe bakery is excellent. Friendly staff. Quick service. Indoor and outdoor seating\nDelicious baked goods... The morning buns are wonderful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Ok, this is in a somewhat seedy area of town ( the Tenderloin has some notoriety). And while you see homeless etc, during the day it is bustling with people.\nThe bakery is excellent. Friendly staff. Quick service. Indoor and outdoor seating\nDelicious baked goods... The morning buns are wonderful.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Barry Sullivan", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/109703427549195961340/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUzbAwtJ3N_d3-gELrQJTaTHoDy8tOgmYDtRqL7nOX0DV0AzFKw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-29T03:09:35.744031877Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGNE1rWkRVSE16V1VSVU16RkZVMGd4WnpZNWRtYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xGNE1rWkRVSE16V1VSVU16RkZVMGd4WnpZNWRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x80858112994842f7:0xac8648260314bc5e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OS1ZWTlNja3BOU1dWRlkybDRjekJsZW05M1kwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Arsicault is home to the best croissants in the country. The croissants are shatteringly flaky on the outside, soft and pillowy within. You can see the layers of buttery goodness, demonstrating good lamination techniques.\n\nI selected the blackberry almond hazelnut croissant and two of the ham and cheese. The ham and cheese is reminiscent of the classic French jambon-beurre, just reimagined in croissant form. I could pick up a subtle whisper of rosemary woven through the savory ham. I can see how Ariscault elevates their baked goods by selecting quality ingredients.\n\nThe blackberry almond hazelnut croissant is a showstopper. The berry jam filling is perfectly balanced by the nuttiness of almond and hazelnut.\n\nAriscault croissants satisfies your cravings for a sweet or savory pastry. Absolutely divine doesn’t begin to cover it. Well worth the visit and wait!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Arsicault is home to the best croissants in the country. The croissants are shatteringly flaky on the outside, soft and pillowy within. You can see the layers of buttery goodness, demonstrating good lamination techniques.\n\nI selected the blackberry almond hazelnut croissant and two of the ham and cheese. The ham and cheese is reminiscent of the classic French jambon-beurre, just reimagined in croissant form. I could pick up a subtle whisper of rosemary woven through the savory ham. I can see how Ariscault elevates their baked goods by selecting quality ingredients.\n\nThe blackberry almond hazelnut croissant is a showstopper. The berry jam filling is perfectly balanced by the nuttiness of almond and hazelnut.\n\nAriscault croissants satisfies your cravings for a sweet or savory pastry. Absolutely divine doesn’t begin to cover it. Well worth the visit and wait!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Sunshine Puppy", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105256590617830121978/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjV7LnIAS7kUOzWJFLKEVAc1YxBccJLFbPzjRZWYorxWc2ULvsU=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-19T13:38:23.581915967Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OS1ZWTlNja3BOU1dWRlkybDRjekJsZW05M1kwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21OS1ZWTlNja3BOU1dWRlkybDRjekJsZW05M1kwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80858112994842f7:0xac8648260314bc5e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvNFZVMVVNVkJwTWpWemVsRkNObFZFZDA5RmNWRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "It's a good thing I live about 2500 miles away from this place. Good lawd.  Everything is divine. It's one of those places where everyone will have a different favorite. For me, it's the chocolate almond croissant and the blackberry almond croissant. But make it your own...just go.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "It's a good thing I live about 2500 miles away from this place. Good lawd.  Everything is divine. It's one of those places where everyone will have a different favorite. For me, it's the chocolate almond croissant and the blackberry almond croissant. But make it your own...just go.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Scot Fishman", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113511273710305955020/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUcIhgXWNRPN_qp6MiWsZuwn8iChBbm2vonK7h1IRbuI38J29eNnw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-14T15:57:32.804600222Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvNFZVMVVNVkJwTWpWemVsRkNObFZFZDA5RmNWRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvNFZVMVVNVkJwTWpWemVsRkNObFZFZDA5RmNWRRAB!2m1!1s0x80858112994842f7:0xac8648260314bc5e"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psaVFqZEpXbGh3VEdZemNteE1iazVRYTNWd2FFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "After all the hype of arsicault, the food was quite disappointing. I only had the savory pastries but they didn't live up to the reputation.\n\nI got the ham and cheese croissant and the bacon savory scone. Texture wise the crossaint was on point. It was crunchy on the outside and soft on the inside. But there was too much fat in the crossaint. It felt very heavy on the stomach.\n\nThe scone was too dense and crumbly. I am not an expert on scones but all in all not worth the exorbitant price. I much prefer Anderson bakery in japan town or juniper for similar fare.\n\nThe service was friendly but brisk which you can't fault them for since it's always packed.\n\nProbably won't revisit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "After all the hype of arsicault, the food was quite disappointing. I only had the savory pastries but they didn't live up to the reputation.\n\nI got the ham and cheese croissant and the bacon savory scone. Texture wise the crossaint was on point. It was crunchy on the outside and soft on the inside. But there was too much fat in the crossaint. It felt very heavy on the stomach.\n\nThe scone was too dense and crumbly. I am not an expert on scones but all in all not worth the exorbitant price. I much prefer Anderson bakery in japan town or juniper for similar fare.\n\nThe service was friendly but brisk which you can't fault them for since it's always packed.\n\nProbably won't revisit.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Akshay Bhagat", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104390713985569466301/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocKsbApZETKIg263PLb-p8ZieV--oCysezAMNYP4fSs45uqV0A=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-12T20:20:00.534372791Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psaVFqZEpXbGh3VEdZemNteE1iazVRYTNWd2FFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2psaVFqZEpXbGh3VEdZemNteE1iazVRYTNWd2FFRRAB!2m1!1s0x80858112994842f7:0xac8648260314bc5e"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ90JImRKBhYARXrwUAyZIhqw/photos/AWCwydhdGqeVXQ3X3SqnbPbOyIPriShj2Wh_bxYxVpSOt-EyMb8vUlfb99MFVWmMMdFaWIpAKm8pEjM_l2Y